name: Interstellar Rat Cage and 4 Jokes
description:
Made in August 2020, at the start of Victoria's second wave of Covid

It's a joke/trash game made for RMIT's game design studio class

Made entirely with 3rd party assets (credits within)

made on Wurundjeri land

---------------------------------------------

Movement: WASD  & Space 

Quit: Alt + F4
